This doesn't work, unfortunately. The permission p that is passed in is the entity:own GRNPermission: GRNPermission{type=entity:own, target=grn::::stream:000000000000000000000003}
That would mean we would need this check in the WildcardPermission class instead. (which we cannot do because it's part of shiro)
I am afraid we need to find a different solution.

